<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Kylie Jenner loves to twin with her young daughter Stormi. </p>

<p>And the 23-yer-old showed there is a strong family resemblance between her and her two-year-old daughter. </p>

<p>The Kylie Cosmetics mogul reposted a side-by-side comparisons of her and Stormi around the same age, to her Instagram Stories on Sunday. </p>

<p>Strong genes: Kylie Jenner showed there is a strong family resemblance between her and her two-year-old daughter, sharing a side-by-side comparison to Instagram on Sunday</p>

<p>All the comparison photos of Stormi were from Kylie's Friday Instagram post of her daughter, that she captioned 'that smile.'</p>

<p>In the first post, Kylie seemed to be around her daughter's age, in a light colored fancy dress and matching tulle headband. </p>

<p>Her dark brown hair was down in loose curls as she beamed a tooth-filled smile at the camera.  </p>

<p>Stormi had her raven tendrils tightly slicked back and pulled up into a ponytail that her mom Kylie decked out in brightly colored barrettes. </p>

<p>Cheesy smile: Another photo of Kylie pulled from the Kardashian-Jenner archives, shows a young reality TV star, with a short blunt bob haircut and thick bangs </p>

<p>Mom mode: Kylie shares Stormi with 28-year-old rapper Travis Scott, whom she split from in October of 2019 </p>

<p>She wore a bright orange tee that had an upside down Reese's Puffs logo printed on it and a pair of comfy grey shorts.</p>

<p>To finish off her casual ensemble, Kylie slipped Stormi's feet into a pair of white socks and some fun multi-colored sneakers.   </p>

<p>Stormi was a natural in front of her mom's camera as she posed for the shots the spacious living room of their Holmby Hills, California mansion.</p>

<p>Another photo of Kylie pulled from the Kardashian-Jenner archives, shows a young reality TV star, with a short blunt bob haircut and thick bangs. </p>

<p>In the eyes: She posed gripping a railing in the black and white photo, with jagged banks and a short bob style, as compared to Stormi climbing up on the couch </p>

<p>The final photo of Kylie seemed to be from a portrait session, and she seems to be just a bit older in age than the others. </p>

<p>She posed gripping a railing in the black and white photo, with jagged banks and a short bob style, as compared to Stormi climbing up on the couch.   </p>

<p>Kylie shares Stormi with 28-year-old rapper Travis Scott, whom she split from in October of 2019.</p>

<p>Despite ceasing their romantic relations, Kylie and Travis have remained civil and committed to co-parenting their little girl. </p>

<p>Original: All the comparison photos of Stormi were from Kylie's Friday Instagram post of her daughter, that she captioned 'that smile'  </p>
